        <div class="commentcontent">
            <p>Google are kinda letting you use it however you please. Step 3, unlocking the boot loader, is not a hack at all.<br />
fastboot is a tool that comes with the Android SDK, and the OEM unlock command is a regular part of that.<br />
Admittedly the warranty voiding nature of it is stupid, as #2 points out.</p>
